linkfm: Links your last.fm account to your account
unlinkfm: Unlinks your last.fm account from your account
listening: Shows what you are listening to
album: Shows what album you are listening to
artist: Shows what artist you are listening to
youalbum: Shows how many times someone has listened to an album you're listening to
youartist: Shows how many times someone has listened to an artist you're listening to
youtrack: Shows how many times someone has listened to a track you're listening to
lyrics: Shows the lyrics of the song you're listening to
love: Loves the song you're listening to
mealbum: Shows how many times you have listened to an album someone else's listening right now
meartist: Shows how many times you have listened to an artist someone else's listening right now
metrack: Shows how many times you have listened to a track someone else's listening right now
crowns: Shows the crown leaderboard on the current group
whoknowsartist: Tries to steal the crown for the artist you're listening to, and shows the leaderboard
globalwhoknows: Shows the global top listeners for an artist
emoji: Changes what emoji shows up when you love a track
last: Shows Last.fm profile information and recent tracks
